<paragraph blockId="0.[146,1431,785,965]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3125557301" collectionCode="F, L" collectorName="Schiede &amp; von Schlechtendal" country="Mexico" location="Botanical Garden of Halle University" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="syntype">
Three samples (
<typeStatus box="[331,437,785,811]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">syntypes</typeStatus>
) all from 
<collectingCountry box="[553,642,785,811]" name="Mexico" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Mexico</collectingCountry>
are listed in the original publication: one collected by 
<collectorName box="[1281,1377,785,811]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Schiede</collectorName>
, one by Mühlenpfordt and one from the herbarium of Lehmann. Because the Schiede collection is the first one listed in the protologue, it is chosen here as the 
<typeStatus box="[708,819,862,888]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The specimen in Halle is preferred, because D. 
<collectionCode box="[1383,1402,862,888]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15707" name="Field Museum of Natural History, Botany Department" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="Herbarium">F</collectionCode>
. 
<collectionCode box="[1406,1427,862,888]" country="Netherlands" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15678" name="Nationaal Herbarium Nederland, Leiden University branch" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" type="Herbarium">L</collectionCode>
. 
<collectorName box="[146,367,901,927]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">von Schlechtendal</collectorName>
was professor of botany and director of the 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03BB90338809E15190B6FDF9DAF7FC09:8ECD77FE8809E15193ACFC38DC79FC53" box="[904,1355,901,927]" country="Mexico" name="Botanical Garden of Halle University" pageId="0" pageNumber="63">Botanical Garden of Halle University</location>
at the time of description of this species (
<bibRefCitation author="Staffleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[555,952,939,965]" pageId="0" pageNumber="63" refId="ref247" refString="Staffleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1967) Taxonomic Literature, vol. 5. International Association for Plant Taxonomy, Utrecht." type="book" year="1967">Staffleu &amp; Cowan 1967: 190-191</bibRefCitation>
)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
